itle":"SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte IV (Raccomandazioni GdS MM)","target":"SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte IV (Raccomandazioni GdS MM)","line":27},{"title":"Troponina Cardiaca ad Alta Sensibilità (hs-cTn)","target":"Troponina Cardiaca ad Alta Sensibilità (hs-cTn)","line":28},{"title":"Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi in Diagnostica di Laboratorio","target":"Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi in Diagnostica di Laboratorio","line":29},{"title":"Controllo di Qualità Interno (CQI)","target":"Controllo di Qualità Interno (CQI)","line":30},{"title":"Validazione e Verifica dei Metodi Analitici","target":"Validazione e Verifica dei Metodi Analitici","line":31},{"title":"Incertezza di Misura","target":"Incertezza di Misura","line":32},{"title":"Fase Preanalitica","target":"Fase Preanalitica","line":33},{"title":"ISO 15189","target":"ISO 15189","line":34},{"title":"Gruppo di Studio sui Marcatori Miocardici (GdS MM) SIPMeL","target":"Gruppo di Studio sui Marcatori Miocardici (GdS MM) SIPMeL","line":39},{"title":"Parte II","target":"SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte II (Indagine GdS MM)","line":57},{"title":"Parte III","target":"SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte III (Ruolo Industria)","line":57},{"title":"Parte IV","target":"SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte IV (Raccomandazioni GdS MM)","line":57}],"metadata":{"type":"source","title":"SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte I (Revisione Letteratura)","created":"2026-06-12","updated":"2026-06-12","tags":["#laboratorio-medico","#source","#troponina","#sipmel"],"status":"developing","address":"c-000052","source_type":"guideline/review","key_claims":["La ricerca PubMed su 'false positive/negative troponin/cTn' ha individuato 106 lavori su 279 totali riguardanti interferenze analitiche dal 1991 a oggi, di cui 46 negli ultimi 5 anni (era hs-cTn).","Le cause di FP/FN di cTn si dividono in pre-analitiche (legate al paziente e al prelievo) e analitiche (legate a strumento, metodo, analita, campione).","Tra le interferenze del paziente: biotina (FP nei metodi competitivi, FN nei sandwich), iperfosfatasemia alcalina, ittero/iperbilirubinemia, emolisi in vivo, digiuno/lipemia.","Tra le interferenze del prelievo/campione: emolisi in vitro (~3% dei campioni, FP o FN secondo il metodo), fibrina (~2,2% dei campioni), anticorpi eterofili/HAMA (fino al 14,8% nei pazienti con sospetta SCA), fattore reumatoide, macrotroponina (fino al 5% con metodo Abbott), autoanticorpi anti-cTn.","Tra le interferenze analitiche: outliers/fliers strumentali (più rari con hs-cTn: 0,13% hs-cTnT, 0,59% hs-cTnI), variabilità tra metodi diversi (cTnT vs cTnI, generazioni diverse, strumenti diversi) con TAE e RCV elevati.","Misure di mitigazione raccomandate: verifica delle performance all'introduzione di un nuovo metodo, verifica giornaliera della calibrazione, calibrazione lotto-lotto, CQI giornaliero su 3 livelli (uno vicino al 99° percentile), controllo sistematico dei reagenti.","Nonostante la letteratura disponibile (incluse linee guida NACB 1999, FDA Alert 2005/2017, raccomandazioni AACC/IFCC 2018), mancano ancora raccomandazioni di buona pratica standardizzate, esaustive e di uso quotidiano per il problema FP/FN di cTn."],"related":["[[SIPMeL]]","[[Gruppo di Studio sui Marcatori Miocardici (GdS MM) SIPMeL]]","[[SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte II (Indagine GdS MM)]]","[[SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte III (Ruolo Industria)]]","[[SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte IV (Raccomandazioni GdS MM)]]","[[Troponina Cardiaca ad Alta Sensibilità (hs-cTn)]]","[[Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi in Diagnostica di Laboratorio]]","[[Controllo di Qualità Interno (CQI)]]","[[Validazione e Verifica dei Metodi Analitici]]","[[Incertezza di Misura]]","[[Fase Preanalitica]]","[[ISO 15189]]"]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:Wiki/sources/SIPMeL - Falsi Positivi e Falsi Negativi di Troponina - Parte I (Revisione Letteratura).md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1fqat7v","at":1781675961126},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.08002576,0.00744368,-0.02572411,0.03002658,-0.0000677,-0.02787852,0.0267602,0.08293846,0.04563113,0.0258744,-0.04594255,-0.10806909,-0.00037551,0.06814959,0.00199526,-0.06844538,0.03175621,-0.01260593,-0.01465764,0.00926547,0.07827844,-0.019,-0.02028439,-0.08842546,0.05431359,0.08006246,-0.01263402,0.03306157,-0.03954189,-0.19929056,0.02250871,0.02428539,-0.0006582,-0.01467976,0.00139368,0.03981199,-0.04149657,0.01533011,0.02445948,0.05398384,0.00086348,0.0581107,-0.01344895,-0.04812062,-0.0070318,-0.07934614,-0.00909036,0.04283828,0.02061871,-0.01664187,-0.04265786,0.03324983,0.03386896,0.07741406,-0.0140593,0.01140272,0.04502523,0.0207535,0.0356529,0.06978039,0.08781999,0.04502116,-0.26816073,0.06871655,0.02980448,0.02038334,-0.04462842,0.03657663,-0.01639573,0.00902419,-0.04710426,-0.00719505,0.03991739,0.01872901,0.03620166,-0.02652488,0.01145975,-0.00039691,0.01434112,-0.02808564,0.04337691,0.04802018,0.01850389,-0.0022625,-0.00087385,0.00560532,0.0503832,0.02953692,0.01987861,-0.02696433,-0.0068216,-0.04678972,0.10599322,0.05169223,-0.00019634,0.05894538,-0.0406452,-0.00428045,-0.04929334,0.07788253,-0.06763865,-0.03386226,-0.01741319,0.00394583,0.0426366,0.04122449,0.00300171,-0.02542873,0.00667441,0.05090941,0.00515077,0.00502847,0.04648474,-0.0242587,-0.06530397,0.03125019,0.06932924,-0.0162159,-0.03133506,0.0388415,-0.02979474,-0.02367177,0.02647256,-0.06500501,0.04209666,-0.07106776,0.02326165,0.0761116,0.0582564,0.01428063,0.10217968,0.03063811,-0.00640585,0.00099044,-0.00012732,-0.04249685,0.01192949,-0.0398925,0.00296072,-0.05185283,-0.02212325,-0.14618881,-0.04055073,-0.05452456,-0.05393164,0.09448483,-0.00236806,0.07532084,0.00047947,-0.00946639,-0.05900121,0.